    <para id="import-auto-id1168584008615">As the bulk-size moves to nano-size, the Melting Point reduces as given below:</para>
    <figure id="import-auto-id1168583484033">
      <media id="import-auto-id1168591661177" alt="">
        <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics12-f806.png" height="64" width="624"/>
      </media>
    </figure>
    <figure id="import-auto-id1168583564805">
