    <para id="import-auto-id1168585804039">In Figure 5.13 it is shown that M.P. of gold particles decreases dramatically as the particle size gets below 5nm.</para>
    <figure id="import-auto-id1168584186554">
      <media id="import-auto-id1168583757123" alt="">
        <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/Picture 2-9271.png" height="415" width="624"/>
      </media>
    </figure>
    <para id="import-auto-id7520990">
      <emphasis effect="bold">Figure 5.13.M.P. of Gold Particles vs Particle Size.</emphasis>
    </para>
    <figure id="import-auto-id1168584018026">
      <media id="import-auto-id1168583699997" alt="">
        <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/Picture 3-ab55.png" height="294" width="626"/>
      </media>
